item.description:
Checkcup Checkcup is a website monitoring tool that fetches the status of websites along with screenshots and active status. It is built using Next.js for the frontend and Puppeteer with Browserless in the backend.
Features Fetches website status including HTTP status code, response time, and active status. Captures screenshots of websites for visual verification. Supports monitoring multiple websites simultaneously. Demo {% embed https://github.com/priyanshuverma-dev/quine-checkcup %}
Live Preview You can view a live preview of Checkcup here.
